OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778234503
OL,3,CIsmaila Sarr strikes again as Crystal
OL,4,CPalace reach Conference League final
OL,6,FCrystal Palace soared into their first
OL,7,FEuropean final after Conference League
OL,8,Ftop scorer Ismaila Sarr scored his
OL,9,Fninth goal in the competition to claim
OL,10,Fa 2-1 semi-final second-leg victory
OL,11,Fover Shakhtar Donetsk.
OL,13,FFor at least a certain generation of
OL,14,FEagles supporters, this was
OL,15,Fundoubtedly the most important fixture
OL,16,Fin nearly 102 years of Selhurst Park
OL,17,Fhistory, one the hosts entered with a
OL,18,F3-1 first-leg advantage and went on to
OL,19,Fsettle the tie 5-2 on aggregate.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
