PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778234503
OL,3,CIsmaila Sarr strikes again as Crystal
OL,4,CPalace reach Conference League final
OL,6,FManager Oliver Glasner hailed Crystal
OL,7,FPalace's "huge European night".
OL,9,F"It was electric," said Glasner. "A
OL,10,Ffantastic atmosphere. A great night at
OL,11,FSelhurst. And of course it was the
OL,12,Fright result and a huge achievement,
OL,13,Fhuge congratulations and credit to the
OL,14,Fplayers.
OL,16,F"The commitment today, the effort, the
OL,17,Fdiscipline, was exceptional, and I
OL,18,Falways believed that we would create
OL,19,Fchances and score goals.
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@^O]qD@AOUqD@RO]qD@bOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
