PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778234503
OL,3,CIsmaila Sarr strikes again as Crystal
OL,4,CPalace reach Conference League final
OL,6,F"At the end we all got the reward with
OL,7,FIsmaila Sarr scoring the goal. A huge
OL,8,Fperformance, and a huge European
OL,9,Fnight."
OL,11,FDaniel Munoz instigated a Pedro
OL,12,FHenrique own goal to open the scoring
OL,13,Fin the 25th minute, cancelled out by
OL,14,FEguinaldo's stylish wake-up call of an
OL,15,Fequaliser before the break.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
