PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778234503
OL,3,CIsmaila Sarr strikes again as Crystal
OL,4,CPalace reach Conference League final
OL,6,FThe instrumental Sarr punched Palace's
OL,7,Ftickets to a Leipzig final against
OL,8,FRayo Vallecano seven minutes into the
OL,9,Fsecond half, extending his scoring
OL,10,Fstreak to five consecutive Conference
OL,11,FLeague matches.
OL,13,FThe visitors, exiled from their home
OL,14,Fcity for 12 years and forced to play
OL,15,Ftheir European "home" games in Poland
OL,16,Fdue to the ongoing war in Ukraine,
OL,17,Femerged from the tunnel wrapped in
OL,18,FUkrainian flags.
OL,26,@wD@POUwD@UO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
