PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778234503
OL,3,CIsmaila Sarr strikes again as Crystal
OL,4,CPalace reach Conference League final
OL,6,FEagles captain Dean Henderson was the
OL,7,Ffirst goalkeeper to be tested,
OL,8,Fcomfortably saving a low Eguinaldo
OL,9,Feffort moments after Kaua Elias
OL,10,Fdirected a shot wide.
OL,12,FYeremy Pino thought he had fired
OL,13,FPalace in front when had the ball in
OL,14,Fthe back of the net in the 10th
OL,15,Fminute, but a VAR check deemed the
OL,16,FSpaniard to be marginally offside in
OL,17,Fthe build-up.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
