PN,40106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778234503
OL,3,CIsmaila Sarr strikes again as Crystal
OL,4,CPalace reach Conference League final
OL,6,FThere was no doubt about the opener,
OL,7,Fwhich began with some good work by
OL,8,FDaichi Kamada to win the ball inside
OL,9,FPalace half after the Eagles absorbed
OL,10,Fa period of pressure.
OL,12,FThe ball was eventually worked to Adam
OL,13,FWharton, who, after a fine run and a
OL,14,Flovely move, was denied by a diving
OL,15,FDmytro Riznyk, who could only parry
OL,16,Fthe ball to his left.
OL,18,FMunoz pounced, and roared with delight
OL,19,Fafter his follow-up took a deflection
OL,20,Foff the unfortunate Pedro Henrique and
OL,21,Fcrossed the line.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778234503
OL,3,CIsmaila Sarr strikes again as Crystal
OL,4,CPalace reach Conference League final
OL,6,FJean-Philippe Mateta and Munoz both
OL,7,Ftried to double Palace's advantage
OL,8,Fbefore Shakhtar reduced the deficit
OL,9,Fback to two goals nine minutes later.
OL,11,FPedro Henrique made some inroads into
OL,12,Fmaking up for his involvement in the
OL,13,Fopener, teeing up Eguinaldo who calmly
OL,14,Fcontrolled the ball then curled it
OL,15,Fbrilliantly into the top corner.
OL,17,FMateta nearly added an acrobatic
OL,18,Fsecond just before the break, clipping
OL,19,Fthe post with a scissor-kick volley,
OL,20,Fmoments after he was the subject of a
OL,21,Fdenied penalty shout from Shakhtar.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
