OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778234503
OL,3,CIsmaila Sarr strikes again as Crystal
OL,4,CPalace reach Conference League final
OL,6,FHenderson stuck out a leg to deny Kaua
OL,7,FElias shortly after the second half
OL,8,Fkicked off, then Sarr fired Palace in
OL,9,Ffront.
OL,11,FThe Senegal international was teed up
OL,12,Fby the sliding Tyrick Mitchell and
OL,13,Fdiverted the cross in via the far
OL,14,Fpost, where Mateta was also lurking.
OL,16,FJorgen Strand Larsen replaced Mateta
OL,17,Fin the 66th minute and had a crack at
OL,18,Fgoal, and Nathaniel Clyne came on for
OL,19,Fhis 250th Palace appearance in a late
OL,20,FOliver Glasner triple substitution.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
